          "locator": "ae57c21cab88e81a",
          "object_type": "theorem",
          "text": "Theorem 1 For any square matrix A with real number entries, A + A ‚Ä≤ is a symmetric matrix and A ‚Äď A ‚Ä≤ is a skew symmetric matrix. Proof Let B = A + A ‚Ä≤ , then",
          "latex": [
            "Theorem 1 For any square matrix A with real number entries, A + A ‚Ä≤ is a symmetric matrix and A ‚Äď A ‚Ä≤ is a skew symmetric matrix. Proof Let B = A + A ‚Ä≤ , then"
          ]
